      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "“What is the will of God for me?”"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "How oft you’ve asked this question."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "It is the church life, corporately,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Where God finds His expression."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Don’t watch the church life from afar,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Or erringly construe it;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Come gaze upon it from within—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "You’ll give your whole life to it."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The church life here is realized,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "’Tis all the Lord intended;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And in this rich experience"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "All further seeking’s ended."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The church life is His glorious will—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Now for yourself begin it."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The surest way to know His will"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Is simply to get in it."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "So let us give our all for this,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And hold ourselves not dearly;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The church life is the will of God,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Let’s take our standing clearly."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Oh, we have found the will of God;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Christ died and rose to win it."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The church life is His glorious will,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And, praise the Lord, we’re in it!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
